title: About
description: My name is Mike. I am an undergraduate at Macquarie University studying a Bachelor of Information Technology, majoring in Software Technology. The languages I am most proficient in are Python and Java. I have had experience with Scala, SQL, C, and Bash. I am currently learning Rust. I am most fascinated by the development and study of programming languages. Presently, I am working through the book 'Crafting Interpreters' and implementing it in Rust.
